
# Project-Name Requirements Testing
## Actors
- Provider P: User
- Customer C: User

### Use Cases
#### 1. Provider: Create provider profile use case (Creating a user profile):
Provider P1 logs in for the first time and creates a profile.
P1 creates new chatrooms Chat1, Chat2, Chat3 with details for describing the chatrooms. P1 is unable to create another chatroom. 

#### 2. Provider: View and subscribe to services (Subscribe to the service, "Tether"):
Provider P1 subscribes to the service, "Tether".
P1 now able to create new chatrooms Chat4.
P1 exits the app.

#### 3. Customer: Create customer profile (Creating a user profile):
Customer C1 logs in for the first time and creates a profile.

#### 4. Customer: Send message in chatrooms
Customer C1 joins chatroom Chat1 and sends a message

#### 5. Customer: Write review
C1 log in and views their subscription.
C1 writes a positive review of service Chat1. C1 exits.

#### 5. Customer: Modify profile
C1 logs in and modifies their profile and uses 3rd party api function (image storage for avatars)
C1 exits.
P1 logs in and views messages and modified profile
P1 exits.
